What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Hydrophilic Coatings Market?

Hydrophilic Coatings Market Analysis

Over the last few years, the coatings business has experienced tremendous growth due to its expanding use in the automotive and medical industries. In addition, the vehicle industry has experienced rapid expansion, which has considerably boosted the market. In 2018, 95,634,593 automobiles were produced, according to the International Organization of Motor Vehicle Manufacturers (OICA). The hydrophilic coatings market will continue to flourish in the future due to the automobile industry's preparedness for a seismic shift brought on by increased production rates. The sector will experience a certain rise in demand, and growing revenues over the forecasted period.

Hydrophilic Coatings Market Size

Global hydrophilic coatings market size was valued at USD 14.65 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 25.18 billion by 2031, with a CAGR of 7.00% during the forecast period of 2024 to 2031.

